snippet.title: Seventh Choir - Biblical Horror Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3033770/Seventh_Choir/

Seventh Choir is a horror game about a hunter who is sent to kill an elk deep within a snow covered swamp. Look to those in the heavens and believe the cry of the seventh choir. A short atmospheric horror game inspired by PS2 hunting games and the Book of Revelation.
